snippet.title: Architect of the Union Trailer
snippet.description:
Adding this game to your Steam wishlist would help us a lot:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2604850/Architect_of_the_Union?utm_source=yt&utm_content=trailer

I'm happy to show the first trailer for my new game "Architect of the Union".

It is a tower defense real-time strategy game where you are in the middle of the action. Based in an apocalyptic Soviet Union.

#ArchitectOfTheUnion #rts #towerdefense #game
